Package org.qualitune.jouleunit

Interface Summary
EnergyProfile An EnergyProfile contains the result of profiling issued by an JouleProfiler.
JouleProfiler Interface for JouleProfilers that can be used to create EnergyProfiles by profiling.
PowerRate Represents one measured power rate of a device under test at a certain point in time.
 

Class Summary
AbstractEnergyProfile Abstract implementation of EnergyProfile.
AbstractJouleProfiler Abstract implementation of JouleProfiler containing platform independent parts.
AbstractPowerRate Abstract implementation of PowerRate.
AbstractProfilerNTimes Abstract implementation of JouleProfiler containing the functionality to profile a Method multiple times.
CompositeEnergyProfile A CompositeEnergyProfile can be used to combine multiple EnergyProfiles that have been profiled in parallel.
CompositeJouleProfiler Composite JouleProfiler implementation to support profiling of multiple devices in parallel.
EnergyProfileComparator Comparator implementation that compares EnergyProfiles w.r.t.
EnergyProfileDurationComparator Comparator implementation that compares EnergyProfiles w.r.t.
JouleAssert Contains assert methods for energy consumption.
JouleUtil JouleUnit Utility class.
SimpleEnergyProfile An SimpleEnergyProfile contains the result of profiling issued by an JouleProfiler.
 

Exception Summary
ProfilingException Thrown if an Exception occurs during profiling.
